Comment: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================PART 1======================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,青青校树 萋萋庭草
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欣沾化雨如膏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,笔砚相亲 晨昏欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔 三年级快要毕业了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,(美术教室)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 今天一整天都听到这首歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也不断听到学长姊练唱的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天头发是不是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶 完全不毛燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被你们发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是该爱漂亮的年纪了 要打理喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈要我好好整理头发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,送了我一把梳子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲 感觉你...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来超有女人味耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为到了该爱漂亮的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,龙二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,青青校树 萋萋庭草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,欣沾化雨如膏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了啊 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还是有点冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说要改到室内呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 反正天气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,到了春天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,与真琴学姊相遇就快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,《电影 学姊是男孩：雨后天晴》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,两位 拜托请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,猜得出你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦 期末考快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是数学真的太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再帮你看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,(图书室)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要套这边的公式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,之前不是也有做过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你听力的分数很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是不时会到国外找你爸爸的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只有听力分数很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别因为听力分数较高就得意过头喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我数学也会努力的 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也要跟妈妈见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 我们今天要去吃烧肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,回家要好好复习喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴你头发长长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,该继续...留长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么做就怎么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,龙二...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你...总是这么挺我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,像是我跟妈妈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我听爸爸说你也有出手帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,总是在背后支持我 从不否定我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真...真琴...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好有龙二在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的让我好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一年级的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是有龙二 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这点让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,堆呼洗 (对不起)...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(大舟屋烧肉)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲 上次送你的梳子好用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好用 我每天都有用喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友还说我看起来跟往常不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不把头发留长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一定很好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈好想看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你小时候本来想帮你留长发的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还说“我讨厌留长发”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时候常把“我不要”挂在嘴边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全没印象耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当时你很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我休假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 就留下来过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么多废话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉麻烦你了 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,既然决定要跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就尽量陪在她身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,棉被要铺在这里是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 剩下的我自己来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那剩下的就交给你们两个年轻人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想叫叫看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,(第3学期期末考成绩单)\N(大我龙二 学年第1名)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(第3学期期末考成绩单)\N(花冈真琴 学年第78名)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(第3学期期末考成绩单)\N(苍井咲 学年第189名)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 全部及格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,名次也上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-我成功了 学姊 师父\N-苍井 回座位上慢慢开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她会...往这边看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她会看过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你往我这边看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我一说所有科目都及格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈就说要好好庆祝 还订了蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想必她很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 你只吃那一点够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我吃太多仙贝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,478)}(爸爸)\N有人打给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是快放春假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来爸爸这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是可以 只是你怎么不早一点说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就只剩奶奶一个人在家耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也说过要跟妈妈见个面的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人在家没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲 妈妈回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们最近有见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先帮你订机票喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah 入境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这边 我在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 没问题...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跟天空的距离很近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 近到手似乎能够到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哈喽 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,OK 你先撑住 我马上赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小...小咲...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在可以出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喔 反正我今天会早点睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那我去一下就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,户上小西 (路上小心)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲 家人来接你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今天啊 爸爸煮了咖喱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲可能会觉得有点辣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开动了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-很好吃吧\N-会不会太辣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-小咲 你这边沾到了\N-爸爸煮的咖喱好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这放了一整个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,胡萝卜也这么大一根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好多块喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我会再买鲸鱼布偶回来给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么妈妈不在了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(只有今天需要工作 抱歉留你在家)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(手机若没通就打去海洋研究所)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我会在这附近晃一晃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,准备去探险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's Go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪儿好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是昨天的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哈...哈喽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,吓...吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要我跟你走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔 不要跑太远喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字叫威尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...My name is Saki Aoi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多指教喔 威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whale
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井 like Whale
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我假装喜欢 会让爸爸很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井 like this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,螃蟹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在问我喜欢螃蟹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是没认真想过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底...真正喜欢什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么才是特别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,会不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是自己的事情耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔你喜欢什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔 是脚踏车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是很帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,应该蛮喜欢天空的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔 你遇到威尔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还带我去他喜欢的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,吃法太淑女的话就不美味了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要像这样 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲 明天爸爸带你去一个有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你一定会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 今天要去看鲸鱼喔 小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟小咲也很喜欢鲸鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很诧异吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然能这么轻松地待在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她们已经习惯人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,比想象的还要大只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很大只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,以一般鲸鱼来说这还算小只的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抹香鲸虽然是齿鲸的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但体型比这些家伙还巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是蓝鲸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,体型可是数倍大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下面好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你会不会冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有哪里不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,口渴不渴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃冰淇淋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都跟你说我没事了 可是我要吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好 对了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那个放在2楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你手机在响哟 研究所打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那待会再接 待会再接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 这是小咲喜欢的鲸鱼布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是新买的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢...鲸鱼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,比以前更喜欢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这雨暂时不会停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲明天就要回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,时间过得好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意跟我一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 反正也不是很远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们跑回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,预备 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别小看中年大叔的体力喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边跟我一起住好吗
Comment: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,======================PART 2======================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,(小咲 欢迎回来 奶奶在姑姑家)\N (回来的话 打个电话给我 —奶奶)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,“奶奶在姑姑家”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“回来的话打个电话给我”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,, (京子姑姑 拨号中)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,京子姑姑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶她啊 身体又不舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.51,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其实没有很严重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果又住院的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲也很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想说让她暂时住在我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还有...你也知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,得跟你说清楚才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.65,0:24:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道奶奶一向很固执
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要考虑跟你妈妈一起住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想跟小咲生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.25,0:24:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得哥哥那边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,姑姑也会协助你的 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来我们一起住好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.22,0:24:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:24:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(京子姑姑)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.69,0:25:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲打来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.15,0:25:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.69,0:25:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.90,0:25:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,睡了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.82,0:25:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有点害怕那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.57,0:25:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,该说她不像个小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.66,0:25:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.29,0:25:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她任何事情都无法自己做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以小咲现在自己一个人在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你等等 我现在过去做晚饭给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.59,0:25:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对 待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.88,0:25:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,(妈妈 LINE 语音)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.55,0:25:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我一个人没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.89,0:25:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.48,0:25:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是妈妈做的特制咖喱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.48,0:25:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.90,0:25:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得寂寞就叫妈妈过来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.11,0:25:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈会立刻赶过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.92,0:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.38,0:26:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.47,0:26:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.11,0:26:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花都盛开了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上周都还没开花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.57,0:26:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是春天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.08,0:26:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是赏花的好日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.12,0:26:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是小吃摊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.71,0:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.54,0:26:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小心别跌倒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.55,0:26:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,苹果糖好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.89,0:26:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.93,0:27:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,素哈(是吗)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.53,0:27:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.79,0:27:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没抓到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.21,0:27:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.96,0:27:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.55,0:27:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,师父好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.59,0:27:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是小吃摊人很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.47,0:27:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有...有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.43,0:27:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么觉得好紧张 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是飞机云耶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.60,0:27:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,学长...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.73,0:27:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看有三条飞过去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.02,0:27:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在...在发光...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.57,0:27:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 飞机云
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.15,0:27:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色很白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.24,0:28:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好刺眼...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.12,0:28:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 因为天气很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.21,0:28:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,飞啊飞啊 找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.68,0:28:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他弄哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.18,0:28:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.51,0:28:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,(镰仓站)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.02,0:28:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,(按钮式红绿灯)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.31,0:28:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,龙二 我问你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.98,0:28:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我看起来有在发光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.66,0:28:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会这么问...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.75,0:28:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别问我这个啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.33,0:28:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.00,0:28:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.71,0:28:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.92,0:28:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,先说好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.18,0:29:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.05,0:29:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.39,0:29:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.06,0:29:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...所以就是那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.98,0:29:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只是该怎么说呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.11,0:29:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好让自己幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.11,0:29:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.20,0:29:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛啦 别露出那种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.70,0:29:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.54,0:29:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都要幸福喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.17,0:29:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.63,0:29:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,(三年级分班公告)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.72,0:29:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.97,0:29:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我没有跟早濑同班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.43,0:29:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.23,0:29:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,早濑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.94,0:29:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,花冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.94,0:29:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三年都同班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.15,0:30:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 好开心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.03,0:30:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(花冈真琴是男的)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.80,0:30:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.13,0:30:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好像跟我们同班呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.05,0:30:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.10,0:30:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,(自习)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.10,0:30:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.94,0:30:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别把笔丢出去啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.11,0:30:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 那是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.90,0:30:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.16,0:30:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.79,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.25,0:30:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,新班级有没有奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.71,0:31:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,盯...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.05,0:31:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.13,0:31:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,班上的同学没什么大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,跟二年级差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.26,0:31:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,到了二三年级要分班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.85,0:31:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.64,0:31:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要选社会组或自然组
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.27,0:31:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.98,0:31:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这次...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.94,0:31:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就不要依赖他们两人 自己解决好了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.82,0:31:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那么接下来是选园艺股长
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.73,0:31:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想做的人请举手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.28,0:31:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么园艺股长
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.82,0:31:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是花冈和藤井
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.45,0:31:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是保健股长
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.34,0:31:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么C班是负责这个花圃
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.76,0:31:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.97,0:31:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.64,0:31:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个秘密不是我散播出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.06,0:31:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,(花冈真琴是男的)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.90,0:32:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.36,0:32:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.11,0:32:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别装成一副受害者的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.74,0:32:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.79,0:32:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是你先做出令人误会的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.58,0:32:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会那样说你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.17,0:32:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,害我一直被捉弄 真的是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.46,0:32:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真要说的话 你才是加害者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.22,0:32:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.38,0:32:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.43,0:32:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.18,0:32:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是男的还留长发
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.56,0:32:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.64,0:32:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.83,0:32:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.62,0:32:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿毛巾过来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.46,0:33:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,适合喔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.71,0:33:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.18,0:33:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.98,0:33:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.23,0:33:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我还差点感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.53,0:33:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你在一起果然没什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.45,0:33:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 藤井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.08,0:33:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,, (升学意向调查表)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.26,0:33:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.22,0:33:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,剩不到一个月就要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.64,0:33:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要仔细思考喔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.06,0:34:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,升学意向...毕业...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.81,0:34:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是应该告白耶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.74,0:34:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再一球
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.11,0:34:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说跟那个学妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.61,0:34:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.87,0:34:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为毕业后就不容易见到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.33,0:34:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.54,0:34:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-那就告白吧 去告白\N -再来 最后一球
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.25,0:34:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.67,0:34:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能快点振作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.96,0:34:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,专心准备考大学啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.59,0:34:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么认定我一定会被打枪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.72,0:34:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.76,0:34:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,告白...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.51,0:34:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.14,0:34:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好巧喔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.60,0:34:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刚结束社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.35,0:34:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.90,0:34:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟刚分班的同学聊得太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.74,0:34:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.03,0:34:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好...明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.50,0:35:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.64,0:35:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...我可以送你回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.81,0:35:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊 你还没换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.35,0:35:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我马上去换
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.65,0:35:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那我在这里等你喔
Comment: 0,0:40:52.43,0:40:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,======================PART 3======================
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.43,0:40:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,(若有讨论升学志愿)\N(或就业的需要 请填写)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.77,0:41:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.82,0:41:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是升学意向调查表吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.82,0:41:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.16,0:41:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也决定好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.07,0:41:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.33,0:41:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.96,0:41:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊你一定没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.67,0:41:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟你有真正喜欢的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.13,0:41:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.68,0:41:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.30,0:41:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.56,0:41:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,外面在下雨 我们找间空教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.48,0:41:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.48,0:41:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学已经决定好跟谁住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.36,0:41:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要转去哪里的学校...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.19,0:41:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还是会选跟妈妈住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.07,0:41:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...我还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.24,0:41:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说下学期要搬过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.24,0:41:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,到现在还没决定 到底要不要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.58,0:42:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能快点做出决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.62,0:42:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互相加油
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.79,0:42:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.93,0:42:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边跟我一起住好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.56,0:42:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.10,0:42:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事当然要看你的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.77,0:42:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟你也不可能大老远搬来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.98,0:42:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不希望这个提议让你感到为难
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.49,0:42:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是当做一个选项啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.70,0:42:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,以你的个性应该能很快适应这里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.70,0:42:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很坚强...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.33,0:42:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 不该这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.49,0:42:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸希望跟你一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.25,0:42:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.75,0:42:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.79,0:42:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑看看
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.72,0:42:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(妈妈 LINE 语音)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.55,0:42:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.60,0:43:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.81,0:43:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.06,0:43:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还是要看小咲的意愿喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.94,0:43:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.65,0:43:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 既然这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.11,0:43:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来妈妈家住看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.37,0:43:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.25,0:43:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.33,0:43:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也能作为下决定的参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.83,0:43:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔 那就这么决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.88,0:43:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下周六日你方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.17,0:43:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好 方便喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.72,0:43:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那到时候见
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.09,0:43:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.43,0:43:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.77,0:43:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这样能做出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.74,0:43:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,记得要带伞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.07,0:43:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.03,0:44:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.41,0:44:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.75,0:44:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.80,0:44:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.51,0:44:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雨呀雨呀 下呀下呀 我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.35,0:44:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着雨伞来接我 我好开心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.94,0:44:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,樱花要谢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.50,0:44:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.59,0:44:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这边...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.75,0:44:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.30,0:44:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉下雨天还要你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.84,0:45:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么啦 反正都坐在公车上
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.97,0:45:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 不要太勉强自己喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.39,0:45:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈可以帮你出计程车钱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.93,0:45:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.81,0:45:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.94,0:45:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.69,0:45:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.98,0:45:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿毛巾给你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.53,0:45:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好 谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.41,0:45:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有妈妈的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.74,0:45:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.33,0:45:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.76,0:45:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.39,0:45:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想说以后可以当你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.35,0:45:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然现在是当杂物间使用
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.15,0:45:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的...房间
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.57,0:45:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还有些行李没整理完
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.99,0:46:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这个房子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.57,0:46:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是以跟小咲生活为前提挑选的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.54,0:46:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.25,0:46:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话会造成你的压力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.04,0:46:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然决定权还是在你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.72,0:46:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,行李就随便放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.26,0:46:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.72,0:46:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该口渴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.93,0:46:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有茶 果汁和热可可 你想喝什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.35,0:46:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...看妈妈推荐什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.69,0:46:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.94,0:46:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那喝热可可怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.44,0:46:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为希望小咲也会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.65,0:46:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就买了这款评价不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.49,0:46:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能合你的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.45,0:46:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 要是跟妈妈在一起生活...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.97,0:47:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.81,0:47:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我午餐的碗盘还没洗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.77,0:47:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦 我完全不会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.65,0:47:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.11,0:47:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没带到今天工作要用的资料\N-你...你等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.65,0:47:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,大概忘在我这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.66,0:47:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.08,0:47:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.58,0:47:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,初...初次见面你好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.21,0:47:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 小咲 这位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.46,0:47:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是本乡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.01,0:47:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我完全忘记这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.38,0:47:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 迟早要告诉她的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.89,0:47:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...他是...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.48,0:47:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.94,0:47:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.15,0:48:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,其实...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.65,0:48:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,本乡先生是住在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.53,0:48:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我常常找他商量许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.08,0:48:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也受到他许多帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.74,0:48:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当然小咲不喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.33,0:48:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他就不会跟我们一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.46,0:48:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我觉得家中还是需要有个男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.42,0:48:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.67,0:48:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能帮上忙 我也会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.43,0:48:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.35,0:48:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.43,0:48:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样 一开始就跟我说不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.85,0:48:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说...说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.11,0:48:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊...你说得没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.19,0:48:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.94,0:48:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.07,0:48:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该吓一大跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.91,0:48:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,来到妈妈家里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.28,0:48:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,却突然进来一个像熊一般的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.08,0:48:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.54,0:49:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为是小偷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.50,0:49:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小偷吗 伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.43,0:49:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系吗 真的不用送你回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.85,0:49:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.31,0:49:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 还有点心
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.31,0:49:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我有伴手礼要让你带回去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.82,0:49:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.94,0:49:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.90,0:49:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈真的非常重视你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.45,0:49:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能了解这点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.78,0:49:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.95,0:49:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.79,0:49:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.33,0:49:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,来 就是这个 带回去吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.63,0:49:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.84,0:49:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,今天打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.55,0:49:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 下次见喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.26,0:49:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.97,0:49:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.48,0:50:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了啊 吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.06,0:50:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃过才回来的 不用准备我的份喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.40,0:50:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我等一下就要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.86,0:50:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.46,0:50:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(升学 就业 其他)
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.61,0:50:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.86,0:50:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.07,0:50:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.07,0:50:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,晚...晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.82,0:50:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 找我有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.08,0:50:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,您正在忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.29,0:51:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.29,0:51:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 学校正在调查升学意向
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.09,0:51:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想找您讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.25,0:51:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,希望外公给我意见
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.55,0:51:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会找我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.63,0:51:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.68,0:51:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得您...很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.65,0:51:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得自己如果也能像您那样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.57,0:51:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被自己喜欢的事物环绕着生活就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.78,0:51:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可是比起被可爱的事物环绕
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.66,0:51:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,更让我觉得了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.12,0:51:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是坦率面对自己想法的外公
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.33,0:51:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的让我觉得很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.88,0:51:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.05,0:51:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.73,0:52:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来了...一大早的按什么电铃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.53,0:52:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.41,0:52:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.83,0:52:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,点心...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.16,0:52:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,做太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.67,0:52:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛给我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.46,0:52:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.30,0:52:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,希望也能珍惜对她的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.02,0:52:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好 调查表都交上来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.60,0:52:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,之后面谈会根据调查表跟你们讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.86,0:52:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得好讨厌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.53,0:52:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这种毕业一分一秒慢慢逼近的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.74,0:52:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.45,0:53:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,早濑同学填什么志愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.24,0:53:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我打算考横滨教育大学
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.20,0:53:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女同学想考的学校也在旁边...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.63,0:53:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要误会喔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.92,0:53:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不是因为距离近才选那所大学喔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.71,0:53:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.72,0:53:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.93,0:53:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只是碰巧我们想考的学校在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.10,0:53:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,早濑同学看起来很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.81,0:53:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.94,0:53:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要...跟苍井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.86,0:53:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.03,0:53:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(我今天在自己教室吃午餐喔)
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.79,0:53:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.96,0:53:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.42,0:53:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,(我知道了 那明天见)
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.97,0:59:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,(我今天也在自己教室吃饭喔)
Comment: 0,0:59:30.26,0:59:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,======================PART 4======================
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.01,0:59:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.76,0:59:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.72,0:59:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在旁边偷看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.97,0:59:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.98,0:59:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想好好见证 让你得以解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.19,0:59:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,解脱...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.02,0:59:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,心情上的解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.61,0:59:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.32,0:59:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.95,0:59:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.11,0:59:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用跑的话应该追得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.20,1:00:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后马上就解脱了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.37,1:00:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.87,1:00:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.79,1:00:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,之前不是说过了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.46,1:00:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会全力阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.38,1:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.64,1:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来...了啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.81,1:00:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以拿毛巾给我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.90,1:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,毛巾是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.69,1:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,毛巾...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.48,1:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.91,1:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.32,1:00:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么大家都知道什么是真正的特别
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.91,1:00:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.29,1:00:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.71,1:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.96,1:00:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.88,1:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.09,1:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.59,1:00:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.72,1:00:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么晚呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.01,1:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.51,1:01:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去跟京子姑姑住喔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.23,1:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我说小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.86,1:01:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了 发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.86,1:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.57,1:01:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能没事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.90,1:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不说出来没有人会知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.62,1:01:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.37,1:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 我好为难喔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.96,1:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.51,1:01:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,(今天吓一跳吧抱歉)\N(下次要跟本乡先生一起吃个饭吗)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.22,1:01:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(小咲 你生气了吗)\N(见个面聊...)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.28,1:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要是妈妈早点来见我就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.87,1:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,像是家长参观日
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.41,1:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或是运动会
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.79,1:02:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,至少打个电话也可以
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.46,1:02:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,即使没有见面
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.92,1:02:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要一直重视我 有把我放在心上就好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.13,1:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要是爸爸做的是更普通的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.80,1:02:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.60,1:02:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把我看得比鲸鱼还要重要
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.64,1:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也会遵守和我的约定
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.60,1:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他能住得更近一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.15,1:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可是事实并非如此
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.02,1:02:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.78,1:02:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲你自己决定就好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.65,1:02:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的真的真的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.70,1:02:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很想跟奶奶一直生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.58,1:02:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 奶奶也是喔
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.29,1:02:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,早安...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.63,1:03:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是花冈吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.84,1:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女同学
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.05,1:03:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.18,1:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,龙二呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.39,1:03:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该先进教室了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.22,1:03:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.43,1:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你在找人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.69,1:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我没有在找人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.90,1:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.52,1:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,(今天跟朋友一起吃喔)\N(喔)
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.32,1:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.95,1:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天也在教室里吃饭
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.87,1:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为...为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.95,1:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女叫我教他功课
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.83,1:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这...这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.88,1:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 真琴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.34,1:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.55,1:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.31,1:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,(对不起 今天也要跟朋友一起吃)
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.97,1:03:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.29,1:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.67,1:04:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.01,1:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.93,1:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.06,1:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.60,1:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子不能好好面对面
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.06,1:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还会见不到你 我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.32,1:04:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.15,1:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.40,1:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不知道该用什么表情
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.53,1:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,该跟你说些什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.79,1:04:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你就忘了那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.83,1:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.08,1:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,继续当和我关系不错的学妹
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.09,1:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.59,1:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.56,1:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.56,1:05:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.44,1:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.02,1:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,下一节课我们一起跷掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.24,1:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是考生耶 可以跷课吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.86,1:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们班下一节是自习
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.91,1:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.53,1:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太贼了吧 我要上数学耶
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.50,1:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会拒绝我的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.37,1:05:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,师父 你果然很讨厌我对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.25,1:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才发现啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.59,1:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.26,1:05:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来对我说要让我的心情解脱吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.01,1:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都说不那么做了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.51,1:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.97,1:05:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟要跟爸爸还是跟妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.60,1:05:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.94,1:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.27,1:06:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还没决定好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.73,1:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你下学期还会在对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.94,1:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个的话...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.95,1:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 以前还满羡慕你的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.83,1:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在无庸置疑地讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.70,1:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.29,1:06:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样 你应该找学姊陪你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.71,1:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.63,1:06:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可是总觉得...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.13,1:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,既然要跷课 还是跟你一起跷比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.48,1:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,师父觉得我该怎么做比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.06,1:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.69,1:06:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己决定
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.53,1:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能尽快做出决定
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.07,1:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.99,1:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.37,1:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.91,1:06:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.33,1:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲你看 是学姊哟
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.29,1:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.13,1:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.88,1:07:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.89,1:07:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.10,1:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.85,1:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我没事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.14,1:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没事怎么会是这种表情
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.52,1:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 完全不像正常的你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.02,1:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.27,1:07:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.11,1:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不说出来没有人会知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.11,1:07:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 真的没事...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.99,1:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.70,1:07:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.49,1:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.58,1:07:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们当你的听众
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.42,1:07:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,转...学...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.05,1:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦 我们不要你转学
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.63,1:07:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 害你们心情也变差了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.55,1:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 不用在意那种事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.93,1:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 不用管我们
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.69,1:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我对自己的事情总是做不出决定
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.73,1:08:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道大家都会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.65,1:08:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.20,1:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.70,1:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,像是未来升学的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.57,1:08:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得要是有什么特别的能让我选
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.41,1:08:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就不必烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.12,1:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.46,1:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,原本想要选护理科系的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.00,1:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但要说是不是非选这科系不可
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.79,1:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我就又不确定了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.25,1:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.84,1:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,中途会改变想法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.34,1:08:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没错...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.43,1:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是对单恋许久的对象
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.64,1:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,突然没了感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.77,1:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲和学姊也是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.89,1:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是特别 什么是真实
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.81,1:08:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.81,1:08:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是在我看来
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.86,1:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲确实一直喜欢真琴学姊哟
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.57,1:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.45,1:09:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼神总是追着他
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.37,1:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还会很大声地叫他
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.16,1:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至跑去追他
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.08,1:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲虽然说自己做不出决定
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.88,1:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是是你发现真琴学姊的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.73,1:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,总之得先想想该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.40,1:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,才能让小咲不要离开
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.82,1:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.57,1:09:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要你离开啦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.61,1:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说啊 小咲
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.36,1:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要离开好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.74,1:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.41,1:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能一直...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.95,1:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你们当好朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.58,1:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.00,1:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是哟
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.42,1:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而且现在...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.51,1:09:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想见真琴学姊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.34,1:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.56,1:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那去找他吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.39,1:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去找他...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.39,1:10:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看他有没有在体育馆
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.73,1:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去一楼找找
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.19,1:10:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,(学姊 你现在在哪里)
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.78,1:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是在我看来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.65,1:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲确实一直喜欢真琴学姊哟
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.32,1:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.49,1:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.25,1:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.13,1:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以这么认定吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.09,1:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在所想的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.89,1:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,或许不寻常
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.64,1:10:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也或许不是真的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.31,1:10:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可是一定要说出来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.65,1:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,否则一定...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.94,1:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定不会知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.90,1:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.40,1:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这边...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.36,1:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.07,1:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.16,1:11:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,(广播室)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.45,1:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这么做没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.12,1:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.66,1:11:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么啊...\N-小咲只要把心里想的说出来就好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.13,1:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.38,1:11:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我到外面帮你看着
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.26,1:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.67,1:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴学姊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.51,1:11:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.26,1:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.18,1:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.56,1:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直渴望拥有“特别”
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.10,1:11:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我至今仍不知道那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.31,1:11:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为遇见真正的“特别”后
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.69,1:11:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,世界会变得闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.23,1:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会变得顺利起来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.78,1:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是谁在做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.53,1:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.08,1:11:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟您讨论未来的出路
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.37,1:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,, 好啊...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.83,1:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但可以晚一点再讨论吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.08,1:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.79,1:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,非得现在才可以
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.29,1:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以拜托老师了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.30,1:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喔...好...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.76,1:12:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我果然很羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.30,1:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我就是找不到
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.31,1:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,即使以为找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.97,1:12:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,却觉得跟自己原本想象的不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.52,1:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,结果更加摇摆不定
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.40,1:12:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,即使等待也没有人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.73,1:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我要的“特别”
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.07,1:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.57,1:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,自己决定
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.32,1:12:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或许不寻常
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.41,1:12:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也或许不是真的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.74,1:12:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.41,1:12:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.16,1:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢真琴学姊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.46,1:12:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 苍井
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.75,1:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.05,1:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 小咲...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.11,1:13:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.12,1:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.18,1:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小...咲...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.97,1:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟妈妈好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.52,1:13:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.15,1:13:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起伤害到你
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.03,1:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.40,1:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想问妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.12,1:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还要丢下我离开
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.00,1:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.87,1:14:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都没来看我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.09,1:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小咲...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.51,1:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请妈妈...请妈妈告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.26,1:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个不合格的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.93,1:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法适应你爸爸国外任职的环境
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.27,1:14:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,(你愿意跟我一起走吗)
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.27,1:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,(对不起)
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.27,1:14:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,家务也做不好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.36,1:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就连照顾你这件事
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.82,1:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也是你奶奶做得比我好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.87,1:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我不在小咲的身边 一定...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.29,1:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.58,1:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我不在的话
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.59,1:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大家才会幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.26,1:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我好几次想回来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.68,1:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是对自己没有信心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.64,1:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,后来之所以敢去找你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.52,1:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为遇见了本乡先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.06,1:15:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,遇见他之后
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.86,1:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,让我萌生想再努力看看的念头
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.65,1:15:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果小咲说不想再跟我有任何关联
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.32,1:15:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那我...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.99,1:15:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 对你来说本乡先生是特别的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.29,1:15:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.71,1:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然...你当然是特别的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.47,1:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.91,1:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 先停一下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.95,1:16:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.37,1:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么周六就能见到奶奶啰
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.92,1:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 学校宿舍离京子姑姑家很近
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.80,1:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了这些事情
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.05,1:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你会去你妈妈那儿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.72,1:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我也犹豫了很久
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.47,1:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,总之现在我只想待在奶奶旁边
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.73,1:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我自己做的决定
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.23,1:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.36,1:16:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是说真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.78,1:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,搬家前一天还来做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.19,1:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,行李都收拾好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.78,1:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.20,1:16:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.53,1:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是前一天才要做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.29,1:16:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别冲太猛 小心会累趴喔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.83,1:16:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可是应该快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.29,1:16:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在大概才一半吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.71,1:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是蝉 有蝉耶
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.38,1:16:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别抓过来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.88,1:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这么可爱耶 你看
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.93,1:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,苍井同学 你好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.98,1:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,云层太厚了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.40,1:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没看到星星呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.94,1:17:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,戳到笑点了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.32,1:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 因为...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.99,1:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我们爬得气喘吁吁的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.66,1:17:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,结果上来完全不晓得是来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.04,1:17:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,连学长也笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.29,1:17:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们半夜聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.91,1:17:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跑来山上看云呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.25,1:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是来看蝉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.88,1:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得看云比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.84,1:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这种日子会不会突然一下子放晴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.22,1:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 也是有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.73,1:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要哭了吗...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.85,1:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我才不会哭
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.31,1:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.11,1:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,明天会是晴天喔
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.19,1:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.75,1:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.05,1:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.47,1:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 小夏
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.80,1:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记带便当了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.89,1:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢 谢谢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.69,1:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.77,1:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来 这个
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.77,1:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这你要带去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.94,1:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.29,1:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.13,1:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.43,1:19:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛像无月之夜般的寂静
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.23,1:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在没有象征的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.27,1:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,假装不知情所洒下的光芒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.11,1:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是有生命的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.03,1:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,取出的时候请小心
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.87,1:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它容易受伤要温柔对待
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.88,1:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,渴望温暖到无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.88,1:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,却不想放任何人察觉
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.76,1:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.22,1:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天都将成为长眠之人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.94,1:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,残缺的月光
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.40,1:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在水面这块画布上
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.23,1:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,描绘出鳞片般闪耀的光辉
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.78,1:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,欠缺了孤独与平凡
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.24,1:20:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人就无法长大
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.95,1:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现实不需要任何润饰
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.58,1:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果想寻找美与光芒的话
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.27,1:20:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有主题的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.57,1:20:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,延伸的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.07,1:20:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只是到常去的医院
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.91,1:20:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看病的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.37,1:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那些再也不会见面的人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.75,1:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的视线刺入内心无法拔除
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.73,1:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,像孤零零漂浮的白云
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.23,1:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,自由自在地
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.90,1:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,随风飘动
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.49,1:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,即使知道自由的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.58,1:21:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从一开始就不存在却仍然前进
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.16,1:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,足迹是不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.50,1:21:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,残缺的月光
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.00,1:21:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在水面这块画布上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.67,1:21:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,描绘出鳞片般闪耀的光辉
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.30,1:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,欠缺了孤独与平凡
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.76,1:21:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人就无法长大
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.47,1:22:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现实不需要任何润饰
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.10,1:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果想寻找美与光芒的话
